The main area of every conference

00:17:57.818 --> 00:18:02.456
is "How do you get into the venue?"

00:18:03.724 --> 00:18:07.294
It gave you specs on doorway widths.

00:18:07.361 --> 00:18:10.930
Again, a lot of the things
that someone with an assistive device

00:18:10.931 --> 00:18:13.633
or disability
wouldn't be impacted by.

00:18:13.634 --> 00:18:16.966
Looking at the front
entrance for doorways,

00:18:17.124 --> 00:18:21.007
automatic doors, paddles,
and it was really cool

00:18:21.008 --> 00:18:22.642
that on the day I took the picture,

