Alex Stein was on the team that year,

00:21:07.141 --> 00:21:12.060
and he attended a conference
at the National Braille Institute.

00:21:13.180 --> 00:21:17.650
Their site had extensive
directions that were turn-by-turn.

00:21:17.651 --> 00:21:20.378
Directions were in a text format.

00:21:20.487 --> 00:21:24.591
I went in, and I did
the same for our venue.

00:21:26.393 --> 00:21:30.129
What you see here is how to get
from the main entrance

00:21:30.130 --> 00:21:33.566
to the resort registration,
