00:21:43.110 --> 00:21:44.677
that we placed on the website.

00:21:44.678 --> 00:21:47.075
It was in a text-only format.

00:21:47.881 --> 00:21:50.483
Also, we provided
a video walkthrough.

00:21:50.484 --> 00:21:53.513
Someone on the team
did that wayfinding

00:21:53.514 --> 00:21:55.689
for our attendees to use.

00:21:55.989 --> 00:21:58.925
We had at least three ways
to figure out

00:21:58.926 --> 00:22:00.593
the location of the venue.

00:22:00.594 --> 00:22:02.663
I would also suggest
getting this information up

00:22:02.664 --> 00:22:03.896
as early as possible because,

00:22:03.897 --> 00:22:06.099
again, you want
to provide all attendees

00:22:06.100 --> 00:22:09.902
as much information as possible
on getting to the venue,

00:22:09.903 --> 00:22:12.105
getting around the venue,
so they can make decisions

00:22:12.106 --> 00:22:13.306
on whether they can make it,

00:22:13.307 --> 00:22:15.842
or they can provide
suggestions or tips

00:22:15.843 --> 00:22:19.096
on how we can make
the information better.

