for neurodivergent attendees.

00:25:05.946 --> 00:25:08.014
This was another suggestion by Ryan,

00:25:08.015 --> 00:25:12.451
in that some people may not feel
comfortable in larger crowds.

00:25:12.452 --> 00:25:16.055
The lower-capacity viewing
rooms are there for them as well,

00:25:16.056 --> 00:25:18.625
but they may want to watch from home,

00:25:18.626 --> 00:25:22.862
so offer some of the sessions
as pre-recorded content,

00:25:22.863 --> 00:25:26.399
so maybe offer the keynote
or the closing remarks

00:25:26.400 --> 00:25:28.136
in a recorded format.

00:25:28.769 --> 00:25:30.670
Another thing that's good in terms

00:25:30.671 --> 00:25:33.005
of usability is providing time points

00:25:33.006 --> 00:25:35.641
